{"id": "art-15321", "label": "Art. 15321", "title": "Art. 15321", "slug": "art-15321", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1362729041\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2047\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1362729041\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 153<sup>21</sup></span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1053318953\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2046\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1053318953\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Actul constitutiv poate dispune c&#259;, în cazuri <span\nclass=SpellE>excep&#355;ionale</span>, justificate prin <span class=SpellE>urgen&#355;a</span>\n<span class=SpellE>situa&#355;iei</span> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> prin\ninteresul <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>, deciziile consiliului\nde <span class=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span> sau ale directoratului pot fi\nluate prin votul unanim exprimat în scris al membrilor, f&#259;r&#259; a mai fi\nnecesar&#259; o întrunire a respectivului organ.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_933425297\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2045\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_933425297\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Nu se poate recurge la procedura prev&#259;zut&#259; la\nalin. (1) în cazul deciziilor consiliului de <span class=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span>\nsau ale directoratului referitoare la <span class=SpellE>situa&#355;iile</span>\nfinanciare anuale ori la capitalul autorizat.</span></p>"}